================================================================================
PROJECT OVERVIEW
================================================================================
PROX CASINO is a cross-platform terminal casino simulator written in Rust.
It uses virtual chips only (no real-money gambling).
Version: 0.2.0
Tech: Rust + ratatui + crossterm + tokio

Repository: /home/charizard/proxcasino

