CURRENT FEATURES
================================================================================

OFFLINE MODE:
  - Blackjack: hit, stand, double down, dealer AI (hits on <17, stands on 17+),
    soft 17 NOT implemented (dealer stands on all 17s), 3:2 blackjack payout,
    streak tracking, win/loss/push tracking
  - Slots: 3-reel, 5 symbols (cherry, lemon, bell, seven, diamond),
    weighted random, payout multipliers (3x, 4x, 7x, 12x, 25x for triples,
    2x for pairs), animated spinning with box-drawn reels, flash on win
  - Dashboard: profile, stats (wins/losses/spins/biggest win), daily bonus
  - Save: atomic JSON saves (write tmp then rename), auto-save on view change
  - Chip formatting: abbreviated (1.2M, 500K, etc.)
  - Daily bonus: 50,000 chips, 1/day

ONLINE MODE:
  - Placeholder only. Client stub, protocol types, no actual networking.

